HEADWORD: Oleate
<hw>O"le*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>ol⟦eacute⟧ate</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A salt of oleic
